      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NANGAR FLY (1) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish third, beaten 2 lengths, (24.29) at Rockhampton. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Capable of going well again. ARMATREE JUDO (5) racing well without winning, placing at her last five runs. Last start finished 2nd on March 28 over 516m at Dubbo behind Boom Bam Ranger beaten 1.5 lengths (29.80) in a Mix. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Deserves a win and gets her chance. CASUAL ALEX (2) has mixed form recently, finishing seventh (18.43) in a Maiden at Taree Super Track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Can feature with the right run. IMPRESS ELSA (8) can return to form after missing the top-three at this circuit last time out.",
